<br>
As always was sitting one side of shrrom patch and single pulling those shrrom and killing them. Then while you're killing... there'll be this suddenly aggro of Dreg or those fungus beast(depend on where i'm leveling) and there's no shout of trains or whatever. What the heck and How the fuk i can aggro them?? I dun bother to think, straight run to the zone near me while shouting train.<br>
<br>
Next moment i zone in, there'll always be some fuker who sit at my campsite or start killing my mob. &quot;Excuse me, this is my camp spot.. i got trained and zoned for last 3 min&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;There's no one here when i came&quot;<br>
&quot;Yes. that's coz i ran to zone with unknown train and you can see that it's a cleared patch, meaning it's not empty without people camping it&quot;<br>
&quot;Who cares.... they might have left just then, doesn't prove anything... anyway i didn't see anyone here when i came&quot;<br>
<br>
All these fuker always came out with the same excuse and guess what.... they are always SK or bard or necro... and this damn PO thought of them actually bringing the train to me to take my camp came.<br>
<br>
Just yesterday, i encounter a real good camp stealer.... Same tthing happen.... was xping in the tunnel towards twiglight zone and got strange aggro from Dreg. Came back to see a bard killing my mob. WTF and it's only like 2 min since i ran and zone back. He stopped after killing one mob and start playing a chrous of replenishment right at the middle of my camp!! I dun bother him and began to pull my mob but every single single fuking mob aggro him coz he's playing his song nd he start  shouting at me WTF am i doing. I told him it's my camp earilier and i'm zoning from train now taking it back.<br>
He reply with real good answer...&quot;I dun care whose camp is it but you shouldn't train me with your pull!!!&quot;....&quot; perhaps you should move since i'm pulling&quot; &quot;Talk to GM about this if you're not happy&quot;.... WTF now it seems i'm in the wrong..and he kept saying about ME training him when i got some impossible aggro from Dreg who are miles away and need to zone coz of that.Anyway... i can no longer do anymore pull with him sitting at my campsite doing song. Instead of wasting hours arguing with him i went in search of new shroom patch( already wasted 15min arguing). And yeah... i'm right... he's been taking that spot for the next 3 hours....and i noticed something... these guys are always ANON....<br>
<br>
Sometimes it's not even about train... you'll sit in a corner doing xp and a whole bunchh of people came and took over it.... just like that... and claiming no one is here. WTF....it's taking over with sheer numbers.<br>
<br>
Real PO...ain't there anymore nice people around anymore? And is there anything wrong with a single mage holding just one shrrom patch?? <p><img src="http://www.scorpz.com/nanidez.jpg">
